text: Sufyan Mehmood (born 21 October 1991) is an Omani cricketer. He played in the 2014 ICC World Cricket League Division Four tournament. He made his Twenty20 International debut for Oman against Hong Kong on 26 November 2015. He made his List A debut for Oman in their three-match series against the United Arab Emirates in October 2016. In August 2018, he was named in Oman's squad for the 2018 Asia Cup Qualifier tournament. In October 2018, he was named in Oman's squad for the 2018 ICC World Cricket League Division Three tournament. In March 2019, he was named in Oman's team for the 2019 ICC World Cricket League Division Two tournament in Namibia. In September 2019, he was named in Oman's squad for the 2019 ICC T20 World Cup Qualifier tournament. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Omani cricketers Category:Oman Twenty20 International cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
